---
title: Seared Salmon & Capsicum Tahini Sauce with Chermoula Potatoes & Radish Slaw
description: Fish royalty is here to grace us with a tasty dinner and delicious sauce. It’s blushing pink salmon tonight with a smokey capsicum sauce drizzled on top to ensure your mouth is watering on the first bite. Spiced spuds and radish slaw bring a burst of flavour to blend with the freshness of the salmon. We bow before this dish!
